  "text": "We compared the performances of five different methods: (1) LA: Haley-Knott linkage analysis [CITATION_1] , (2) LDLA: the regression LDLA method in this work (equation 13), (3) LD decay: LDLA regression by equation [CITATION_2] , that is, ignoring the v* terms, (4) two-marker: regression on twomarker haplotypes (i.e., association analysis), and (5) an IBD method [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , which computes IBD among founders based on all markers (Lee, pers. comm.).",
